723696f-a.title: Manhattan: Vandam Street - 6th Avenue
723696f-a.text:
13 Van Dam Street, north side, west of Sixth Avenue, showing the 3 story building occupying this site and portions of the adjoining structures (No's 11 and 15). View No. 2 shows
the gateway entrance to No. 11.
